## What Is Bookmark AI?

<div class="my-8 p-6 bg-teal-50 border-l-4 border-teal-500">

**Bookmark AI** is an AI-powered website builder that uses an AI assistant (named AIDA) to generate websites based on user prompts.

**KEY CLAIMS:**
- Build a website in 2 minutes
- AI designs your site automatically
- No design skills required
- E-commerce included
- Responsive design

**REALITY:** The AI can generate a basic site quickly, but it rarely looks professional or complete without significant manual editing.

